{
  "stem": "2713.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was afraid at first, but then she said all right, because otherwise, we all had to go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Didn't take long-- half an hour, half an hour, maybe 3/4 of an hour after we left Mr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Novak.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a Pole there who recognized me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He didn't recognize my sister, but he recognized me because he most probably used to come to our place to buy suits.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I begged him to let me go, and he said-- I said to him that I am not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, you-- how can you say you are not Jewish?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You live there and there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he knew exactly where I lived, so I couldn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was-- I could see what the end is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was screaming, I get for you a kilo of sugar, and I will watch you being killed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is-- this is a peasant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I could see that it was very bad, so I whispered to my sister, Celina-- I whispered to her, look, can you see the cross-- across the road?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because I knew the area very well there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she said yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, look, you run there, and then when I see that you are already there, I will start running, because I could run better than she could.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I saw that she was there already, I start running because he was with a horse and a buggy on two-- two wheels.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I run away, but he was after me with the horse, and he start-- the horse start jumping.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I-- when I was running, he start screaming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were little huts from Poles living all around on the land.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
